name: TD Select Short Term Corporate Bond Ladder ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of TD Select Short Term Corporate Bond Ladder ETF (the Fund) is to seek to earn a high rate of interest income while preserving capital through exposure to the performance of a diversified portfolio of primarily Canadian investment-grade corporate bonds divided into groupings with staggered maturities from approximately one to five years. In seeking to achieve this objective, the Fund uses fundamental credit research and quantitative screens to select the corporate bonds. The Fund may also invest in non-investment-grade bonds and/or foreign securities to enhance total returns.
